This directory contains many of the configurations that the NCAR RDA THREDDS data server needs.  

This is housed at GitHub in order to have an offsite copy of the catalogs which take a considerable amount of time to fine tune.  This will also allow for quick updating to mirrored TDS.

catalog_*.xml files are copied to $CATALINA_HOME/content/thredds

Need to restart tomcat6 after a change has been made "/etc/init.d/tomcat6 restart"

http://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/thredds/v4.5/tds/reference/collections/GribCollections.html
